Designed and deployed a 3-microservice architecture (Node.js + Python FastAPI) on AWS.

Implemented containerization (Docker) and orchestration (Kubernetes) with autoscaling (HPA).

Automated deployments via GitHub Actions, AWS ECR, and Kubernetes manifests.

Configured ALB + NGINX Ingress Controller for HTTP routing, AWS RDS for relational data, and MongoDB Atlas for NoSQL.

Integrated AWS SSM Parameter Store and Kubernetes Secrets for secure credentials management.

Monitored application health with Prometheus, Grafana, and CloudWatch.